                    📋 Key Takeaways (1-Page PDF)
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.calix.com/content/dam/calix/AI_Leadership_Playbook_Key_Take-Aways1.pdf" target="_blank" class="download-btn download-btn-secondary" id="downloadFull">
